data.description: Huge newly constructed home at an affordable price! This beautiful home offers plenty of charm and boasts over 2,500 sqft including 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Featuring desirable interior upgrades including stainless steel appliances and lvp flooring. This rare Hayden floor plan is no longer built in the community, and this one happens to sit on a more private lot than others. Liberty offers a community pool and sidewalks throughout the neighborhood, making this the perfect family home. Conveniently located to great schools and entertainment. Call for more information or to schedule a showing today!
